<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This message is used to send information about the status of a device or equipment from one application to another (e.g., automated device to a Laboratory Automation System). The status update can be sent unsolicited or as a response to the trigger "Automated Equipment Status Request."</p>
</div>
